OL,3,CMan wore all 13 shirts at the 'same
OL,4,Ctime to avoid paying for hold baggage'
OL,6,FPhil Lisle, from Cardiff, had
OL,7,Ftravelled from Bristol to Benidorm
OL,8,Fwith EasyJet for a 60th birthday
OL,9,Fcelebration with his friends last
OL,10,Fmonth when he was charged at Bristol
OL,11,FAirport for the weight of his holdall
OL,12,Fleather bag.JMr Lisle said he was
OL,13,F"baffled" when staff informed him
OL,14,F"he'd have to pay #48 because his bag
OL,15,Fwas slightly protruding from a metal
OL,16,Fbox" used to determine whether hand
OL,17,Fluggage can qualify for free boarding.
