OL,3,CMan wore all 13 shirts at the 'same
OL,4,Ctime to avoid paying for hold baggage'
OL,6,FHe said: "The stewardesses were
OL,7,Flaughing their heads off when I was
OL,8,Fgetting it all off. They were great to
OL,9,Fbe fair.
OL,11,F"I said: 'Come on, you can't throw me
OL,12,Foff now.' And they just laughed. Fair
OL,13,Fplay to them, at the end when we were
OL,14,Fgetting off in Bristol one of them
OL,15,Fsaid: 'Don't forget all your shirts."
